origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'GreenTransportAPI.analyze_operational_data', 'description': 'This function analyzes the operational data for specified green transport projects within a given time range.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'project_ids', 'type': 'LIST', 'description': 'A list of project IDs for which to analyze operational data.'}, {'name': 'time_range', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time range for which to analyze operational data, e.g., last_year, last_quarter.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'operational_analysis', 'description': 'An analysis of the operational data for the specified projects and time range.'}]}
请用以下格式进行回复:
想法: 你这一步的目标
动作: 你要调用的API名称
动作参数: JSON格式的参数输入,全部写在一行
调用工具 GreenTransportAPI.analyze_operational_data, 它的参数输入如下: 'project_ids'是['123', '456'], 'time_range'是'last_year'.
